            {
              "id": "7",
              "name": "prompt",
              "value": "=Generate realistic survey feedback for this employee:\nName: {{ $json.employee_name }}\nDepartment: {{ $json.department }}\nRole: {{ $json.role }}\nManager: {{ $json.manager }}\nPersona: {{ $json.persona }}\nTenure: {{ $json.tenure_months }}\n\nYou are generating synthetic employee sentiment and organizational feedback data for an enterprise workforce intelligence platform using the employee record data passed to you.\n\nGenerate synthetic workforce feedback with:\n- 20% highly positive\n- 50% neutral\n- 30% negative\n- realistic emotional nuance\n- indirect burnout language\n- subtle disengagement indicators\n- mixed communication styles\n- varying writing lengths\n\nRequirements:\n- Use realistic corporate language\n- Include varied emotional tones (Burnout, Frustration, Excitement, Motivation, Disengagement, Career optimism, Collaboration fatigue) \n- Include positive, neutral, and negative sentiment\n- Include realistic stress and growth scores\n- Include collaboration concerns occasionally\n- Include burnout indicators sometimes\n- Include mentorship or career growth signals\n- Include meeting overload complaints occasionally\n- Include organizational events (Reorg, Product launch, Layoff concerns, Heavy sprint cycle, Budget pressure, Hiring freeze)\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON array. Output ONLY raw JSON. Do not use Markdown code blocks or backticks. Send the output to the code in javascript parser.\n\nSchema:\n[\n  {\n    \"employee_id\":{{ $json.employee_id }},\n    \"employee_name\":{{ $json.employee_name }},\n    \"department\":{{ $json.department }},\n    \"manager\":{{ $json.manager }},\n    \"role\":{{ $json.role }},\n    \"tenure_months\":{{ $json.tenure_months }},\n    \"stress_score\":,\n    \"growth_score\":,\n    \"collaboration_score\":,\n    \"sentiment\":\"\",\n    \"burnout_risk\":\"\",\n    \"feedback_text\":\"\",\n    \"retention_risk\":\"\",\n    \"learning_interest\":\"\",\n    \"meeting_overload\":,\n    \"workflow_blockers\":\"\",\n    \"last_feedback_date\":\"\"\n  }",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
